            </ul>
        </change>
        <change version="0.7.1">
            <ul xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
                <li>Fix problem with parsing of inline strong - <a href="https://github.com/eXist-db/exist-markdown/pull/11">#11</a></li>
